        "dataNature": "ordinal"
      },
      "archiveReason": "Documented narratively in wp_eins (Antworttypen → Ranking) but never operationalized: no blessed example, no qwacback.answerType, no <QuestionTypeBlock> reference, no agreed cross-tool encoding (kobo stores 1 space-separated column; LimeSurvey type R stores N positional columns; DDI analyst expectation is N ordinal vars per item). Re-introduce as composite:rank when (a) cross-tool fan-out is implemented and (b) wp_eins gains a <QuestionTypeBlock> example.",
      "archivedSince": "2026-05-20"
    }
